{"tid":2320624,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝光頭警長劉澤基同會長林志偉支持唔封關, 先可以令咁多警察中由尼泊爾引入既尼泊爾病毒株武漢肺炎,真正領悟病者既感受","createTime":"2020-12-11T03:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T15:11:49.000Z","uid":179775,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"209c527ecd67738d3dd69f0ee09728d0fd268741","tid":2320624,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:12:17.000Z","msg":"相信佢地唔會做逃兵<br />\n好好封鎖麗晶同其他爆肺炎既地方<br />\n有警察在市民最前線<br />\n真係好感動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zcYogU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zcYogU.jpg&h=a37797c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ziPPuWV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FziPPuWV.jpg&h=355f12ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n光頭警長劉澤基，在微博上「呼應」屈穎妍，大罵請病假護士是「魔鬼」、「垃圾」，「不用懷疑了，這班逃兵醫護在請病假前，已經表明心迹。<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">可能有一日他們病倒了，才知今日自己的所作所為，才知道作為病者的感受。</span></span>但說真的他們明白感受也沒有用，壞了心腸的醫護怎樣變也是魔鬼一隻。 根本就是垃圾，他們的行為影響了一直在前線拼命的醫護英雄」。"},{"pid":"b556d722782c8add93eac8223ce7ab476cf50d9d","tid":2320624,"uid":357031,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14070410ff20f94f3df0d91c12c17ff0ab23e81","tid":2320624,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b556d722782c8add93eac8223ce7ab476cf50d9d","tid":2320624,"uid":357031,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc455b39924a71c730e53669a39e877906b29b7","tid":2320624,"uid":179775,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl